cs.CR, cs.IOT, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.DC 

The paper deals with cryptography libraries specifically aimed for application in the field of Internet of Things (IoT), which falls under the category of cs.IOT. The paper also discusses the various algorithms contained within the libraries, which is a characteristic of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper provides a comprehensive repository for reference to the various cryptography libraries, which is a characteristic of cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also deals with the performance analysis of the libraries, which is a characteristic of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
